{"tid":1809234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【不明肺炎】【集中帖】所有有做野既區議員","createTime":"2020-01-03T02:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:25:43.000Z","uid":212944,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6028b75fa558e0c7ac1183cc02466f7ad42b4c","tid":1809234,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"1. 屯門區議員 ─ 聯署<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/80995057_2308336355934971_8888319645228990464_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ohc=gIPInJUSjWQAQmATPXH0EoLKZPDAU4gG6i9gYBuhbrtO6UoHIceqooAGw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=1e9584908521ba6493304d37c5fe5e58&amp;oe=5E958AC4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F80995057_2308336355934971_8888319645228990464_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ohc%3DgIPInJUSjWQAQmATPXH0EoLKZPDAU4gG6i9gYBuhbrtO6UoHIceqooAGw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D1e9584908521ba6493304d37c5fe5e58%26oe%3D5E958AC4&h=7d979bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔要求衛生署盡快公開交代事件〕<br />\n<br />\n不明感染個案入侵本港，事件令一眾市民人心惶惶。森仔聯同屯門十一素人去信衛生署，要求當局盡快公開交代事件，以釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n同時，市民亦需要保持警覺，時刻注重個人衛生，保障自己及家人健康。<br />\n<br />\n黃丹晴 Lemon Wong<br />\n巫堃泰 Michael Mo<br />\n張可森<br />\nTak-yuen Wong 王德源<br />\n曾振興<br />\n潘智鍵 Gary Poon<br />\n李家偉 Kawai Lee<br />\n龍門居民 曾錦榮<br />\n田景梁灝文<br />\n張贊華（里奧）<br />\n羅焯勇 Cheukyunglaw"},{"pid":"df3c9da4180653d6b38706c28188f82125d81a48","tid":1809234,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"2. 旺角東區議員林兆彬 ─ 街站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgnLZdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgnLZdS.png&h=45e234c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4da5e6673976a307eeed2f4ec16bf2644b30810c","tid":1809234,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"希望區議員可以快D作出反應<br />\n派下口罩又好<br />\n提下大家勤洗手都好"},{"pid":"96931f29298fe224c2d24920f1a21a0933a